r": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "Cover Art_Landscape_2560x144020.png", "id": "6675375442547548", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982461_6675375449214214_374955904288494240_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=TtAqis_tqRQQ7kNvgGU2D6H&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=AnhL_2TZdBSajieDbRSlb-0&oh=00_AYBoiecsQYGEPCNGWsDhD2tUU437HfKGdh8ami2PPRW8uQ&oe=66ED647A"}, "display_name": "Nightmare Tag", "keywords": [], "long_description": "A multiplayer PvP Horror Experience packed full of INTENSE CHASES & JUMP SCARES! In Nightmare tag, you can either be one of the mortal humans trying to run and hide for your life, geared only with your flashgun, scanner, and a variety of surreal attachments. Or, become the blood-hungry monster to terrify your friends! Nightmare tag will have you and your friends screaming, laughing, yelling, & sweating until your headset runs out of power! \n\nBECOME THE NIGHTMARE: \n- Find & chase your friends before they escape the liminal Dreamscape!\n- Unique controller motion movement to use your claws to run, jump, and tear apart humans!\n- Track & hunt humans using your many abilities!\n- Eliminate all the humans to win as the monster\n\nRUN FOR YOUR LIFE: \n- Join your friends as you Run and Hide from the Nightmare!\n- Hide by being completely motionless, making you invisible to the monster\n- Physical Running Motion allows you to sprint when you are found and need to escape!\n- Your flashgun is your only weapon, use it to see where you're going and stun the monster!\n- Use your scanner to locate the monster, reunite with other humans, find power-ups, and find the objective.\n- Complete the objective win as the humans!\n\nMULTIPLE GAME MODES:\n- VHS Run\n- Quick Tag\n- Elimination (requires General Admission)\n- Capture the Fruit (requires General Admission)\n+ A variety of game and map settings to shake things up!\n\nGENERAL ADMISSION (IAP):\n- Unlock 6 more zones\n- Play Elimination and Capture 